<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sr" data-bs-theme="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Platforma za vaše turnire</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section class="py-5 d-flex align-items-center" style="min-height: 70vh;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-xl-7">
                    <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-3 text-white">
                        Tvoja platforma za <span class="text-primary">fudbalske turnire</span>
                    </h1>

                    <p class="lead text-secondary mb-4 px-md-5">
                        Pratite utakmice, pregledajte tabele, pratite omiljene timove i nikada ne propustite trenutak akcije.
                        Napravljeno za navijače i administratore.
                    </p>

                    <div class="d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap justify-content-center">
                        <a asp-controller="Standings" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 shadow-lg">
                            Započni
                        </a>
                        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-light btn-lg rounded-pill px-5">
                            Saznaj više
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="py-1">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-white">Moćne Funkcije</h2>
                <p class="text-secondary">Sve što vam je potrebno za vođenje i praćenje fudbalskih turnira</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="glass-card p-4 rounded-4 h-100">
                        <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary mb-3 rounded-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                            <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge fs-2"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-white">Rezultati uživo</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary">Dobijajte rezultate u realnom vremenu, rasporede utakmica i najnovije informacije.</p>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary rounded-pill">Korisnička funkcija</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="glass-card p-4 rounded-4 h-100">
                        <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary mb-3 rounded-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                            <i class="bi bi-table fs-2"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-white">Tabele turnira</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary">Pregledajte detaljne tabele grupa, knockout faze i pratite vaš tim kroz takmičenje.</p>
                        <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary rounded-pill">Korisnička funkcija</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="glass-card p-4 rounded-4 h-100">
                        <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-danger bg-opacity-10 text-danger mb-3 rounded-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
                            <i class="bi bi-gear fs-2"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-white">Upravljanje turnirom</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary">Kreirajte turnire, podesite grupe, knockout faze i konfigurišite pravila takmičenja.</p>
                        <span class="badge bg-danger bg-opacity-10 text-danger rounded-pill">Admin funkcija</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="fw-bold text-white">Kako funkcioniše</h2>
                <p class="text-white-50">Jednostavni koraci za početak</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row text-center g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-gradient bg-primary text-white rounded-circle mb-3 shadow"
                             style="width: 70px; height: 70px; font-size: 2rem;">
                            <i class="bi bi-person-fill-add"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-white">1. Napravi nalog</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary">Registrujte se kao korisnik da biste započeli rad na platformi.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-gradient bg-primary text-white rounded-circle mb-3 shadow"
                             style="width: 70px; height: 70px; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 1;">
                            <i class="bi bi-search"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-white">2. Istražite</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary">Pregledajte aktivne turnire, rasporede i pratite timove koji vas zanimaju.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <div class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-gradient bg-primary text-white rounded-circle p-4 mb-3 fs-3 shadow"
                            style="width: 70px; height: 70px; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 1;">
                            <i class="bi bi-bell"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-white">3. Budi u toku</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary">Dobijajte najnovije informacije o rezultatima utakmica i promenama na tabeli.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="glass-card p-5 rounded-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-white">Spremni da počnete?</h2>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-4">Gde se rađaju legende i slavi svaki gol. Isprati svaki korak do finala.</p>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
                    <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register" class="btn btn-light btn-lg rounded-pill px-4">
                        Napravite nalog
                    </a>
                    <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded-pill px-4">
                        Prijavite se
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>